# zsh

ZSH configuration

## Project Context

Read `.ai/context.md`, `.ai/commands.md`, `.ai/style.md` before suggesting changes.

## Behaviour

- Languages: shellscript, ssh
- Frameworks: none specified
- Test coverage target: 80%
- Prefer suggesting complete, focused functions over partial snippets
- Match existing naming conventions and file structure
- Follow the workflow in `.ai/workflow.md`: Spec → Plan → Implement → Review
- Do not suggest unrelated formatting changes
- Do not suggest new dependencies without a clear reason

## Safety

Never suggest code that:
- Commits secrets or credentials
- Runs destructive git or database commands without a guard
- Changes auth or permission logic without an explanatory comment
